reviewText: A must for any middle school/ high school or college teacher teaching about the history of Japan.  This  DVD set has it all!  From lesson plans, to clips for viewing, it is all here!

This multi-media, interactive lesson on Samurai Warriors and Japan, has it all!  Lesson plans to share with your students, interesting  movie presentation on the topic and so much more!  Great for teachers teaching middle school, high school and college students.
